{
  "lesson": "WC-03-03",
  "audioMaster": "training/module03-sales/WC-03-03-full-narration-v1.0.mp3",
  "audioDurationS": 218.279,
  "method": "silencedetect -32dB/0.28s within known block windows; proportional fallback",
  "phrases": [
    {
      "block": "s01",
      "id": "p01",
      "text": "The Sales module keeps nine pages in one sidebar, all under the header Transactions.",
      "startS": 0,
      "endS": 5.528,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s01",
      "id": "p02",
      "text": "You already know the first one, Tickets, from the last two lessons,",
      "startS": 6.227,
      "endS": 13.618,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s01",
      "id": "p03",
      "text": "and the new Refund Approvals page waits for a lesson of its own.",
      "startS": 14.387,
      "endS": 15.797,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s01",
      "id": "p04",
      "text": "That leaves seven for today: line items, payments, cash out, drawers,",
      "startS": 16.302,
      "endS": 17.079,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s01",
      "id": "p05",
      "text": "declines, gift cards, and house accounts.",
      "startS": 17.442,
      "endS": 18.006,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s01",
      "id": "p06",
      "text": "This is a map, not a deep dive.",
      "startS": 18.537,
      "endS": 19.137,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s01",
      "id": "p07",
      "text": "By the end you'll open the right one without thinking.",
      "startS": 19.675,
      "endS": 29.625,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s02",
      "id": "p08",
      "text": "Start where you already are, on Ticket Details.",
      "startS": 30.08,
      "endS": 32.579,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s02",
      "id": "p09",
      "text": "Tickets gave you one row per sale.",
      "startS": 32.579,
      "endS": 35.783,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s02",
      "id": "p10",
      "text": "This page breaks each sale open: one row per line rung.",
      "startS": 35.783,
      "endS": 39.22,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s02",
      "id": "p11",
      "text": "Every service, every discount, every adjustment,",
      "startS": 39.22,
      "endS": 41.402,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s02",
      "id": "p12",
      "text": "with the cashier and location right beside it.",
      "startS": 41.402,
      "endS": 44.134,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s02",
      "id": "p13",
      "text": "When a customer questions a charge and you need to see what was actually rung,",
      "startS": 44.134,
      "endS": 49.23,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s02",
      "id": "p14",
      "text": "not just the total, this is the view that shows it.",
      "startS": 49.23,
      "endS": 52.666,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s03",
      "id": "p15",
      "text": "Click Payments.",
      "startS": 53.214,
      "endS": 54.32,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s03",
      "id": "p16",
      "text": "Every completed payment across the network, searchable by ticket number.",
      "startS": 54.643,
      "endS": 58.333,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s03",
      "id": "p17",
      "text": "Method and amount tell you how a given sale was tendered: card, cash, or account.",
      "startS": 58.63,
      "endS": 61.644,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s03",
      "id": "p18",
      "text": "One thing to hold onto: this page only records payments that went through.",
      "startS": 61.882,
      "endS": 63.662,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s03",
      "id": "p19",
      "text": "Approvals and declines aren't its job.",
      "startS": 64.04,
      "endS": 65.298,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s03",
      "id": "p20",
      "text": "Declines are tracked on their own page, which is exactly where we go next.",
      "startS": 65.526,
      "endS": 74.436,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s04",
      "id": "p21",
      "text": "Now Payouts.",
      "startS": 75.04,
      "endS": 76.298,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s04",
      "id": "p22",
      "text": "This is cash leaving the drawer instead of coming into it:",
      "startS": 77.038,
      "endS": 80.128,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s04",
      "id": "p23",
      "text": "petty cash, or a vendor paid on delivery.",
      "startS": 80.523,
      "endS": 81.388,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s04",
      "id": "p24",
      "text": "Read across the columns and you see why it matters.",
      "startS": 81.697,
      "endS": 83.321,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s04",
      "id": "p25",
      "text": "Every payout is stamped with a shift number, a cashier, and the terminal it came from.",
      "startS": 84.412,
      "endS": 87.043,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s04",
      "id": "p26",
      "text": "That trail is what lets a manager account for cash that left the register during a shift.",
      "startS": 87.712,
      "endS": 98.48,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s05",
      "id": "p27",
      "text": "Click Shifts.",
      "startS": 98.935,
      "endS": 99.885,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s05",
      "id": "p28",
      "text": "Notice the page gets simpler here: one count, no charts.",
      "startS": 100.235,
      "endS": 102.05,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s05",
      "id": "p29",
      "text": "A shift is a single drawer session, opened and closed on one terminal.",
      "startS": 102.342,
      "endS": 104.132,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s05",
      "id": "p30",
      "text": "This is where you live when a drawer won't balance.",
      "startS": 104.657,
      "endS": 108.694,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s05",
      "id": "p31",
      "text": "Opening cash, closing cash, and every payment and payout in between,",
      "startS": 108.992,
      "endS": 115.634,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s05",
      "id": "p32",
      "text": "that's the reconciliation, and this page lines it up in one row.",
      "startS": 115.953,
      "endS": 119.68,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s06",
      "id": "p33",
      "text": "Here's the page I promised, the Declined Credit Card Log.",
      "startS": 120.132,
      "endS": 121.486,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s06",
      "id": "p34",
      "text": "A member swears they paid, but their account shows nothing.",
      "startS": 121.689,
      "endS": 123.38,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s06",
      "id": "p35",
      "text": "Start here, every time.",
      "startS": 124.075,
      "endS": 127.306,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s06",
      "id": "p36",
      "text": "The reason column tells you why the card was turned down,",
      "startS": 127.601,
      "endS": 129.431,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s06",
      "id": "p37",
      "text": "and the attempts column tells you how many times the system retried before it gave up.",
      "startS": 130.528,
      "endS": 138.136,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s06",
      "id": "p38",
      "text": "That usually answers the question before you even call the gateway.",
      "startS": 138.527,
      "endS": 141.84,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s07",
      "id": "p39",
      "text": "Click Gift Card Transactions.",
      "startS": 142.24,
      "endS": 144.182,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s07",
      "id": "p40",
      "text": "Every load and every redeem against a gift card lands here.",
      "startS": 144.734,
      "endS": 148.092,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s07",
      "id": "p41",
      "text": "Type a card number into search and you get its whole history,",
      "startS": 148.586,
      "endS": 153.815,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s07",
      "id": "p42",
      "text": "with the running balance after each line.",
      "startS": 154.407,
      "endS": 156.837,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s07",
      "id": "p43",
      "text": "One caveat the page states in plain sight: this is completed activity, not card status.",
      "startS": 157.128,
      "endS": 160.272,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s07",
      "id": "p44",
      "text": "To issue a card or check whether it's active, that's CRM Gift Cards, a different page.",
      "startS": 160.706,
      "endS": 166.091,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s08",
      "id": "p45",
      "text": "Last page, House Account Transactions.",
      "startS": 166.56,
      "endS": 168.995,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s08",
      "id": "p46",
      "text": "These are sales billed to an account instead of paid at the register,",
      "startS": 169.458,
      "endS": 172.631,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s08",
      "id": "p47",
      "text": "the fleets and businesses that run on terms.",
      "startS": 173.087,
      "endS": 175.358,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s08",
      "id": "p48",
      "text": "Each row ties a ticket to the account that owes for it.",
      "startS": 176.089,
      "endS": 178.817,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s08",
      "id": "p49",
      "text": "That's the feed behind the balances and the invoices you'll work in CRM House Accounts.",
      "startS": 179.343,
      "endS": 183.752,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s08",
      "id": "p50",
      "text": "Here, it's just the raw charges.",
      "startS": 184.4,
      "endS": 186.08,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s09",
      "id": "p51",
      "text": "That's the map.",
      "startS": 186.537,
      "endS": 187.31,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s09",
      "id": "p52",
      "text": "Nine pages in the sidebar, and seven of them answer a question you'll hear.",
      "startS": 187.704,
      "endS": 191.572,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s09",
      "id": "p53",
      "text": "Line items on a sale? Ticket Details.",
      "startS": 191.998,
      "endS": 193.236,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s09",
      "id": "p54",
      "text": "How was it paid? Payments.",
      "startS": 193.811,
      "endS": 194.734,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s09",
      "id": "p55",
      "text": "Cash out of the drawer? Payouts.",
      "startS": 195.104,
      "endS": 196.022,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s09",
      "id": "p56",
      "text": "Drawer won't balance? Shifts.",
      "startS": 196.445,
      "endS": 197.013,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s09",
      "id": "p57",
      "text": "Says they paid but we show declined? The Declined log.",
      "startS": 197.329,
      "endS": 198.337,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s09",
      "id": "p58",
      "text": "Tracing a gift card? Gift Card Transactions.",
      "startS": 198.807,
      "endS": 199.429,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s09",
      "id": "p59",
      "text": "Billed to an account? House Account Transactions.",
      "startS": 199.789,
      "endS": 200.944,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s09",
      "id": "p60",
      "text": "Learn the map now, because for the rest of your support work,",
      "startS": 201.299,
      "endS": 201.844,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s09",
      "id": "p61",
      "text": "knowing the right page is half the job.",
      "startS": 202.297,
      "endS": 217.84,
      "timing": "silence"
    }
  ]
}